description_0: A dolphin is swimming in an aquarium in the middle of the image. The dolphin's body is slightly curved up diagonally toward the top right corner of the image. The dolphin's head is slightly tilted up to the surface of the water. The dolphin's mouth is wide open, the front of the dolphin's mouth is sticking out of the surface of water. There is an uneven rock wall on the right side of the image behind the dolphin, the rock wall ends at the left side of the image and a stone wall begins. There is a gray cement ball at the base of the wall. The ripples of the water are magnifying light onto the dolphin, the wall, and the gray cement ball.
description_1: A diver is inside a large fish tank feeding a whale shark along with smaller fish inside an aquarium. A stingray is also in the tank behind the diver. The diver is wearing an all black dive suit, a scuba tank, and a face mask. Bubbles are coming out of the tank and mask. The person is in front of the whale shark, and a school of the smaller fish are underneath the shark. Another diver is near the bottom of the image with bubbles coming out of their tank. Light rays are shining through the water in the tank.
